title: War of the Roses: He Lives in the Snowmobile Trailer
description: Ben & Kari are dating. Kari's ex boyfriend needed a place to live and she asked Ben if he could live with them. Obviously he said no but jokingly said he could live in their snowmobile trailer. What happened next is INSANE!
